Alhaji Ibrahim Tanko is the Coordinator, National Association Of Government Approved Freight Forwarders (NAGAFF), 100 percent Compliance Team. In this interaction with journalists in Lagos, he spoke about the relationship between the NAGAFF and the Association for Nigerian Licensed Customs Agent (ANLCA), saying it was cordial. ANDREW UTULU was there. Excerpts: Can tell us the thrust of this briefing? Yes, the Customs Area Controller, Apapa Command invited me and told me there is a petition against me from one John Offorbuike. He allowed me to go through the petition which he had sent to the Enforcement Unit of Customs. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! So, I proceeded to enforcement, made a statement. It was addressed to the Area Controller. But why I have called you here is for you to understand that this petition is baseless. If you can recall, recently, we had a synergy agreement with the Association of Nigeria Licensed Customs Agents (ANLCA). At that meeting, the President of ANLCA was with us at the National Association of Government Approved Freight Forwarders headquarters (NAGAFF Village), in Apapa, Lagos. When I got this petition, I called the attention of ANLCA to it. The President of ANLCA was shocked to hear this. AMJON Holds Workshop On Blue Economy SON Needs Strong FG Backing To Succeed – MAN Boss I want you to understand that the synergy between NAGAFF and ANLCA still stand irrespective of the baseless petition. There is no division between ANLCA and NAGAFF. This issue has to do with part of the bad eggs we are talking about in the system. Even in NAGAFF, we also have people like that. So, we cannot be surprised if we find people like that in ANLCA. Tell us more about the petition? He said, I Ibrahim Tanko, and my team, the 100 percent Compliance Team, have been harassing Customs officers, we are intimidating Customs Officers, we are extorting Customs officers, we are blackmailing Customs officers. He made mention of three terminals, the Mid Maritime terminal, Demka terminal and AML bonded terminal. Let’s look at in this perspective. First and foremost, the visit we made to these terminals, we did with members of the press. We were on tour of the terminals. I did not go there alone. Since that time, I have never gone there. Whatever transpired there, the press should bear me witness. I did not intimidate, harass or extorted any Custom officer. It is laughable that an armless civilian like me will intimidate an armed Customs officer? How would somebody without gun harass somebody with gun? How would somebody who has no power of arrest, intimidate or harass an officer who has power of arrest and with gun without being arrested. But to me, I have nothing against Offorbuike as a person. Before the Compliance Team came to being, while I was Vice President Western Zone of NAGAFF, the Founder of NAGAFF asked me to go and work with him. I, called him more than three times. In fact, I even went to the Customs Long Room to meet him, and I told him that I don’t have anything against him. So, what are the issues? The issue there is that people are out there with sole purpose of causing confusion. I want you to remember that the synergy between NAGAFF and ANLCA was the second time. The first time, the same thing happened, but because, if we are not careful in treating the issues, everybody went his way. This time around, we cannot allow that to happen. Tell us about what the 100 percent compliance team does? Since the inauguration of the team, we have never harassed or intimidated anybody, be it Customs Officer of any government agency. We are still working on the importers and our members, telling them to do the right thing. We have never accused any Customs officer, be it corrupt or doing wrong thing. If we did, let the person come out and tell the world. It is suppressing that a civilian, a clearing agent has now become a spokesman to the Customs. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION